divs: Sighting Details1At home and finding out what the dogs were barking at. 2A feeling of beingwatched and something telling me to look up. 3Mars. 4Joy and excitement. 5shapecigar with 5 lights connected in a row, surrounded by red glow. Then moved higher and changed shape again to a ball with 2diagonal tails from the backbottom. 6Did not lose site of object. It movedacross sky to another position in SW quadrent.
